elements.label: Instruction Header > Main Instruction
elements.description: Bold gray text 'Great. Now choose a daily goal.' centrally positioned below the progress bar
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly frames the header text, with minimal extra white space and good alignment. No correction needed.

elements.label: Progress Bar > Status Indicator
elements.description: Yellow horizontal progress bar at the top of the screen showing completion status, positioned below the device status bar and next to a back arrow
elements.explanation: Box tightly frames the yellow progress bar, with only a slight overextension to the right. Accurate position and size for the described element.

elements.label: Progress Bar > Back Arrow
elements.description: Gray left-pointing arrow positioned to the left of the progress bar, allowing navigation to previous screens
elements.explanation: Box covers the back arrow well with minor padding on either side, matching description and visual alignment.

component_description: Detection results for Daily Goal Selection List

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Casual Option > Label
elements.description: Text 'Casual' on the left side of the first row option in the daily goal selection list
elements.explanation: Box contains both the 'Casual' label and the associated time info, but reasonably frames the entire row. Good positional coverage, but not tightly focused on just the label.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Casual Option > Time Commitment
elements.description: Text '5 min / day' on the right side of the row containing the 'Casual' option
elements.explanation: Box accurately captures the '5 min / day' text with an appropriately tight fit.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Regular Option > Label
elements.description: Text 'Regular' on the left side of the second row option in the daily goal selection list
elements.explanation: Box contains both the 'Regular' label and the time info, but covers the full row as per design. Not tightly focused just on the label but coverage is reasonable.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Regular Option > Time Commitment
elements.description: Text '10 min / day' on the right side of the row containing the 'Regular' option
elements.explanation: Box accurately contains the '10 min / day' text, minimal extra space.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Intense Option > Label
elements.description: Text 'Intense' on the left side of the fourth row option in the daily goal selection list
elements.explanation: Box contains the entire 'Intense' row including the time commitment; not tightly cropped to label but covers its function.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Intense Option > Time Commitment
elements.description: Text '20 min / day' on the right side of the row containing the 'Intense' option
elements.explanation: Box closely matches and frames the '20 min / day' text with very accurate boundaries.

component_description: Detection results for Primary Continue Button

elements.label: Primary Continue Button > Label
elements.description: White uppercase text 'CONTINUE' centered on a bright green button at the bottom of the screen
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly frames the 'CONTINUE' text horizontally and vertically, with only 2-3 pixels extra padding at top and bottom, yielding high accuracy.

elements.label: Primary Continue Button > Container
elements.description: Bright green rectangular button with rounded corners spanning the width of the screen with padding on both sides, positioned near the bottom of the interface
elements.explanation: Bounding box nearly perfectly encloses the button container, aligning well with all four edges and masking only a minimal shadow at the corners.

component_name: Daily Goal Selection List > Serious Option
component_description: Detection results for Daily Goal Selection List > Serious Option

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Serious Option > Label
elements.description: Text 'Serious' on the left side of the third row option that has a light blue background highlight
elements.explanation: The original box covers the entire highlighted row instead of just the 'Serious' label; tightened to only encompass the text on the left.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Serious Option > Time Commitment
elements.description: Text '15 min / day' on the right side of the light blue highlighted row containing the 'Serious' option
elements.explanation: Original box covered the whole row; corrected to focus on the '15 min / day' text on the right.

elements.label: Daily Goal Selection List > Serious Option > Selection Highlight
elements.description: Light blue background highlighting the entire row containing the 'Serious' option and '15 min / day' text
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly fits the highlighted row as described; only a slight (almost negligible) top/bottom margin overdraw.

component_description: Detection results for Answer Construction Area

elements.label: Answer Construction Area > Selected Words
elements.description: Four connected pill-shaped buttons reading 'Are you a cat' in sequence, shown with dark text on light backgrounds
elements.explanation: Original box only covers one word button ('Are'). Adjusted to encompass all four connected selected word buttons as described.

elements.label: Answer Construction Area > Input Field
elements.description: Empty white rectangular area spanning the width of the screen below the selected word buttons
elements.explanation: Box incorrectly spans the entire screen. Adjusted to tightly fit the empty input field directly below the selected word buttons.

component_description: Detection results for Feedback and Continue Section

elements.label: Feedback and Continue Section > Feedback Message
elements.description: Green text 'Correct!' in the lower portion of the screen against a light green background
elements.explanation: Box covers all feedback elements but is wider than just the 'Correct!' message and includes the icon as well; reasonably accurate for broad feedback area.

elements.label: Feedback and Continue Section > Feedback Icon
elements.description: Small icon to the right of the 'Correct!' text within the light green feedback bar
elements.explanation: Original box was misplaced, covering an area above the actual icon. Corrected to tightly fit the icon's true location next to the 'Correct!' text.

elements.label: Feedback and Continue Section > Continue Button
elements.description: Bright green rectangular button with white uppercase text 'CONTINUE' spanning the width of the screen at the bottom
elements.explanation: Box matches the green 'CONTINUE' button very closely, with precise horizontal and vertical fit.

elements.label: Word Bank > Option 1
elements.description: Pill-shaped gray button with 'horse' text positioned on the left side of the word bank row
elements.explanation: Box tightly fits the pill-shaped 'horse' button with slight horizontal extra space, generally very accurate.

elements.label: Word Bank > Option 2
elements.description: Pill-shaped gray button with 'girl' text positioned in the center-left of the word bank row
elements.explanation: Box fits the 'girl' button, but is slightly too narrow and could extend more to the right side for full coverage.

elements.label: Word Bank > Option 3
elements.description: Pill-shaped gray button with 'It's' text positioned in the center of the word bank row
elements.explanation: Box accurately covers the 'It's' button with minor vertical misalignment; mostly correct.

elements.label: Word Bank > Option 4
elements.description: Pill-shaped gray button with 'woman' text positioned on the right side of the word bank row
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the 'woman' button; fully covers the intended element.

elements.label: Word Bank > Additional Buttons
elements.description: Several light gray circular buttons without text, distributed between and below the word option buttons
elements.explanation: Box covers one of the additional circular buttons but not all; accuracy is reduced because the element described as 'several' is only partly covered. Slightly too large vertically, but usable for a single button.

elements.label: Instruction Header > Title
elements.description: Bold dark text 'Write this in English' positioned at the top of the screen below the status bar
elements.explanation: Original box encompasses the entire screen and is not specific to the title text. Suggested a tight fit around the actual title just below the status bar.

elements.label: Instruction Header > Close Button
elements.description: Gray X icon in the top-left corner of the screen, used for navigation
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely fits the X icon in the top-left corner. Minor discrepancies present but it accurately targets the close button.

elements.label: Instruction Header > Search Bar
elements.description: Horizontal gray rounded rectangle field below the title, appearing inactive with no visible text
elements.explanation: Original box includes part of the close button area and is poorly aligned. Suggested new coordinates enclose the search bar directly underneath the title.

elements.label: Prompt Card > Character
elements.description: Cartoon illustration with black hair bun and orange shirt in the left portion of the prompt area
elements.explanation: Box is well-aligned and tightly fits the cartoon character's head and bun, slightly missing the lower shirt area.

elements.label: Prompt Card > Speech Bubble
elements.description: White rounded speech bubble containing the French text 'Tu es un chat ?'
elements.explanation: Bounding box very accurately frames the entire speech bubble, including the text and audio icon.

elements.label: Prompt Card > Audio Button
elements.description: Blue speaker icon inside the speech bubble, positioned to the left of the French text
elements.explanation: Box tightly contains the blue speaker icon with minimal extra space; visually accurate.

component_description: Detection results for Lesson Completion Summary

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > XP Container
elements.description: Yellow rectangular container with rounded corners positioned in the bottom half of the screen on the left side, containing experience point information.
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the actual yellow XP container with a small margin difference on the right edge. No correction is needed.

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > XP Label
elements.description: Small gray text 'TOTAL XP' at the top portion of the yellow rectangular container, labeling the reward type.
elements.explanation: Bounding box is significantly larger than the 'TOTAL XP' label itself, extending well below the text into the value area. A tighter fit would improve accuracy but it still encompasses the label.

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > XP Value
elements.description: Yellow text '15' with an upward-pointing arrow icon to its left, displayed in the center of the yellow container showing earned points.
elements.explanation: Original box is too large, extending well outside the actual value area and to the right past the container. Suggested box now tightly fits the XP number and icon.

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > Performance Container
elements.description: Green rectangular container with rounded corners positioned in the bottom half of the screen on the right side, containing performance metrics.
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the performance container's main area. May miss a few pixels at the bottom, but overall alignment is very good.

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > Performance Label
elements.description: Small text 'AMAZING' at the top portion of the green rectangular container, describing the achievement level.
elements.explanation: Box is oversized and includes value and container; suggested correction tightly fits the 'AMAZING' label in the green area.

elements.label: Lesson Completion Summary > Performance Value
elements.description: Green text '100%' with a target/bullseye icon to its left, displayed in the center of the green container showing perfect score.
elements.explanation: Original bounding box includes label area and extends well below the value. Suggested coordinates now fit just the value and icon, matching the description.

component_description: Detection results for Completion Celebration Section

elements.label: Completion Celebration Section > Mascot Characters
elements.description: Two colorful cartoon characters shown in the middle of the screen - a green duck-like figure on the left and a character with dark hair, pink top and mint green bottom on the right with arm raised in celebration pose. Small red items scattered nearby. Positioned above the completion message.
elements.explanation: Bounding box tightly encloses both mascot characters and related items, with minimal excess margin and appropriate vertical and horizontal fit.

elements.label: Completion Celebration Section > Loading/Success Icon
elements.description: Small purple starburst/asterisk symbol displayed in the upper middle portion of the white screen background, consisting of several thin lines radiating outward.
elements.explanation: Bounding box precisely covers the starburst icon; very slight margin but otherwise highly accurate and visually well-centered.

elements.label: Completion Celebration Section > Status Text
elements.description: Yellow text 'Lesson Complete!' centered horizontally beneath the cartoon characters, indicating successful completion status.
elements.explanation: Bounding box very closely fits the yellow text with minimal padding and good top/bottom margins, accurately reflecting the intended element.

elements.label: Continue Button > Button
elements.description: Wide green rectangular button with rounded corners at the bottom of the screen, containing white uppercase text 'CONTINUE' centered within it.
elements.explanation: Bounding box closely matches the green 'CONTINUE' button with only very minor padding outside the rounded corners; no correction necessary.
